Attribute.name: speed rating
Attribute.commentInRDBMS: Alphabetic value that matches to the maximum MPH the tire is capable of reaching without damage to the tire.

Attribute.name: load range
Attribute.commentInRDBMS: Alphabetic ply rating of the tire.

Attribute.name: revs mile
Attribute.commentInRDBMS: Tire's revolutions per mile.

Attribute.name: revs km
Attribute.commentInRDBMS: Tire's revolutions per kilometer.

Attribute.name: min rim width
Attribute.commentInRDBMS: Minimum width of the wheel the tire is designed to be mounted on.

Attribute.name: max rim width
Attribute.commentInRDBMS: Maximum width of the wheel the tire is designed to be mounted on.

Attribute.name: single max load
Attribute.commentInRDBMS: Numerical value (in lbs.) of the single load index.

Attribute.name: single max psi
Attribute.commentInRDBMS: Unused field. Currently using ud_capacity_psi field instead.

Attribute.name: dual max load
Attribute.commentInRDBMS: Numerical value (in lbs.) of the dual load index.

Attribute.name: dual max psi
Attribute.commentInRDBMS: Unused field. Currently using ud_capacity_psi field instead.

Attribute.name: tread depth
Attribute.commentInRDBMS: Verticle measurement between the top of the tire's tread rubber and bottom of the tire's deepest groove in 1/32 inch (currently unused).

Attribute.name: type
Attribute.commentInRDBMS: Custom field used for Tools Group to identify item type.

Attribute.name: section width
Attribute.commentInRDBMS: 3 digit numerical portion of the tire size that identifies the cross section of a tire in millimeters.

Attribute.name: aspect ratio
Attribute.commentInRDBMS: Percentage ratio of the tire's sidewall height from rim to tread of the section width of the tire.

Attribute.name: utqg wear
Attribute.commentInRDBMS: Numerical value of the UTQG (Uniform Tire Quality Grading) rating.

Attribute.name: utqg traction
Attribute.commentInRDBMS: Alphabetic value of the traction portion of the UTQG (Uniform Tire Quality Grading) rating.

Attribute.name: utqg tem
Attribute.commentInRDBMS: Alphabetic value of the temperature portion of the UTQG (Uniform Tire Quality Grading) rating.

Attribute.name: sidewall
Attribute.commentInRDBMS: Condensed description of the visual appearance of the tire sidewall (side portion of the tire).

Attribute.name: warranty
Attribute.commentInRDBMS: Manufacturer's Tire Mileage warranty.

Attribute.name: warranty km
Attribute.commentInRDBMS: Manufacturer's Tire Mileage warranty in KM.

Attribute.name: country
Attribute.commentInRDBMS: Country of manufacture.

Attribute.name: run flat
Attribute.commentInRDBMS: Flag to identify tires which can operate upto 50miles at 50mph at 0 (zero) psi.

Attribute.name: oem
Attribute.commentInRDBMS: Identifies if a tire is Original Equipment Manufacturer (OEM).

Attribute.name: uhp
Attribute.commentInRDBMS: Identifies if the tire is Ultra High Performance (UHP; V-speed rated or higher).

Attribute.name: rim diameter
Attribute.commentInRDBMS: Tire diameter measured in inches.

Attribute.name: winter
Attribute.commentInRDBMS: Identifies is a tire is rated for Winter use.

Attribute.name: load ind
Attribute.commentInRDBMS: Numerical value used to determine relative load carrying capabilities.

Attribute.name: utqg
Attribute.commentInRDBMS: Uniform Tire Quality Grading rating.

Attribute.name: service type
Attribute.commentInRDBMS: Type of vehical/service for which the tire was designed for.

Attribute.name: full size
Attribute.commentInRDBMS: Complete tire size as described by the manufacturer.

Attribute.name: load speed
Attribute.commentInRDBMS: Combination of the complete load index and speed rating.

Attribute.name: core
Attribute.commentInRDBMS: Core item of all TLCs.

Attribute.name: net special
Attribute.commentInRDBMS: Flag to identify if tire is on a pricing special from supplier (currently unused).

Attribute.name: net special price
Attribute.commentInRDBMS: Reduced cost of the tire if tire on net special (currently unused).

Attribute.name: pending dd
Attribute.commentInRDBMS: pending discontinuation flag (currently unused).

Attribute.name: tier
Attribute.commentInRDBMS: Numerical value of the tier (currently unused; use class1_id instead).

Attribute.name: overall diameter
Attribute.commentInRDBMS: Outer diameter of the tire measured in the center of the tread.

Attribute.name: tread
Attribute.commentInRDBMS: Verticle measurement between the top of the tire's tread rubber and bottom of the tire's deepest groove in 1/32 inch.

Attribute.name: capacity psi
Attribute.commentInRDBMS: Represents maximum capacity of the tire that can be inflated to under cold pressure. Stamped on the sidewall of the tire.

Attribute.name: dual load index
Attribute.commentInRDBMS: Numerical value used to determine relative load carrying capabilities in dual application.

Attribute.name: dd
Attribute.commentInRDBMS: Flag to identify discontinued item (at item level).

Attribute.name: tread pattern
Attribute.commentInRDBMS: Tread pattern (currently unused).

Attribute.name: studdable
Attribute.commentInRDBMS: Represents if the tire can accept studs.

Attribute.name: foam
Attribute.commentInRDBMS: Goodyear sound detonating technology.

Attribute.name: application
Attribute.commentInRDBMS: Identifies whether a tire is consumer, commercial or industrial.

Attribute.name: sales tier
Attribute.commentInRDBMS: Same as class1_id also knowns as brand_group_id (currently unused).

Attribute.name: extended desc
Attribute.commentInRDBMS: Extended/full description of the item’s pattern

Attribute.name: default product group
Attribute.commentInRDBMS: Indicates if an item is Tire or non-tire

Attribute.name: msf
Attribute.commentInRDBMS: mountain snowflake applicable or not

Attribute.name: season type
Attribute.commentInRDBMS: Season type associated with the tire
